{"tid":2227741,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"何依婷靚相被登色情網 慘變「小仙女Baby」接客","createTime":"2020-10-03T04:45:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-03T07:10:54.000Z","uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"78112bc876edf48de6fb8cfa4e518bfea95628d6","tid":2227741,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T04:45:20.000Z","msg":"26歲何依婷是2017年港姐亞軍，工作機會不斷，早前在《機場特警》豪放坐楊明大髀、比堅尼洗車，成功引起網民討論。備受力捧的何依婷的靚相近日竟出現在一色情網站上，以「小仙女Baby」之名拉客，更注明可提供絲襪制服誘惑服務，網頁已有超過八千次瀏覽，相當受歡迎﹗<img src=\"https://imgs.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/cb5a0f6c-3131-4e68-8d31-b02d92eb5329_11241128875f76cf6b0a78b.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.orientalsunday.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F10%2Fcb5a0f6c-3131-4e68-8d31-b02d92eb5329_11241128875f76cf6b0a78b.jpeg&h=868c6c2f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a47e9d6dc861a63b1eeb2181fa62c894e65a4697","tid":2227741,"uid":71166,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T04:46:43.000Z","msg":"提供特別服務唔使五嚿水<br />\n上位中的何依婷竟然在色情網站上出現，以「小仙女Baby」名稱，並登了數張何依婷的相片，相中的何依婷著上喱士上衣下襯窄身短裙，輕撥秀髮，據網站所提供的資料相當露骨，以「後生靚索女」、「天使面孔」、「小小蠻腰」、「修長美腿」、「翹翹靚籮」、「服務周到」等，並指可提供特別服務，如絲襪制服誘惑、泰式服務收費$488。<img src=\"https://imgs.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/2a8180ec-ec3b-425c-95ea-2e3ac9a9e5df_14288182445f76cf694cefe-1024x594.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.orientalsunday.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F10%2F2a8180ec-ec3b-425c-95ea-2e3ac9a9e5df_14288182445f76cf694cefe-1024x594.jpeg&h=04fa962a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"55f6804f67df6cba38285e1e88d95e33503dcfb1","tid":2227741,"uid":65984,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T04:48:47.000Z","msg":"可能真係佢呢"},{"pid":"936418465b5531805253b6e8378ee3b6232b6d0e","tid":2227741,"uid":262674,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T04:51:58.000Z","msg":"証明佢係雞樣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1804f4c5